doc: Hi. So, I was enjoying a game per usual and now suddenly it no longer wants to run.
Step 1: Open Tomodachi Life from the main menu.

It was working perfectly fine before. But during emulation I went to the menu, clicked Emulation > Restart, Citra closed. I reopen it manually, go to reopen the game, and it crashed. It has crashed every time I try to load the game since then. I have tried everything. I have tried reinstalling Citra, i have tried reinstalling the ROM, I have tried restarting my Mac. Nothing works. I tried to start the game while running a different game, and now that game crashes Citra too. I have no idea what to do. Please help.
